vent that the Company/Website is acquired by or merged or amalgamated with  a third party entity, we reserve the right, in any of these circumstances, to  transfer or assign the information we have collected from our Users as part of  such merger, acquisition, sale, or other change of control. <br>\n  We  are a company based in India. By browsing/using the Website, You hereby  acknowledge that the Company is not responsible or liable in any manner to  comply with any local laws of Your territory except India with respect to the Website. </p>\n<div><br>\n  <strong>Disclaimer:</strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Company  is a service provider, and through its logistics partners, collect the goods  ordered by the customers and have them delivered to the customers and  facilitates the collection and remittance of payments. Company disclaims any and  all liability if the vendor fails to make the requested goods available for  delivery. </div>',	'2021-10-14 17:41:31',	'2021-10-14 17:41:31'),
